<div id="review_4176945812" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/4176945812" />
    <a title="Bruna  ♛" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/64692335-bruna"><img alt="Bruna  ♛" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1616671447p2/64692335.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/4176945812?book_show_action=true">Jan 18, 2022</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Bruna  ♛" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Bruna  ♛" href="/user/show/64692335-bruna">Bruna  ♛</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Leather Bound " href="/book/show/6747570-the-vampire-chronicles">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/64692335-bruna?shelf=3-stars-aka-it-was-ok">3-stars-aka-it-was-ok</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/64692335-bruna?shelf=first-book-in-a-series">first-book-in-a-series</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/64692335-bruna?shelf=fantasy">fantasy</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/64692335-bruna?shelf=urban-fantasy">urban-fantasy</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/64692335-bruna?shelf=completed-series">completed-series</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/64692335-bruna?shelf=lgbtq-plus-books">lgbtq-plus-books</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/64692335-bruna?shelf=adult">adult</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/64692335-bruna?shelf=classics">classics</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/64692335-bruna?shelf=vampires">vampires</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4176945812" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13282947346816271615">✯ [3/5] ✯<br/><br/>I EXPECTED SO MUCH MORE.<br/><br/>The Interview With The Vampire: 3/5 - I actually enjoyed this one as much as the movie, and that means not as much. I think Claudia is really strange, Louis calls her a sexual being and this bothers me a little bit you know? And Louis is a bad narrator....<br/><br/>The Vampire Lestat: 4/5 - Lestat is my fave, this book was such a LGBT one, really it shows they have male lovers, I respect the author for this.<br/><br/>The Queen of The Damned: 2.5/5 - sorry I didn&apos;t get super excited </span>
  <span id="freeText13282947346816271615" style="display:none">✯ [3/5] ✯<br /><br />I EXPECTED SO MUCH MORE.<br /><br />The Interview With The Vampire: 3/5 - I actually enjoyed this one as much as the movie, and that means not as much. I think Claudia is really strange, Louis calls her a sexual being and this bothers me a little bit you know? And Louis is a bad narrator....<br /><br />The Vampire Lestat: 4/5 - Lestat is my fave, this book was such a LGBT one, really it shows they have male lovers, I respect the author for this.<br /><br />The Queen of The Damned: 2.5/5 - sorry I didn't get super excited for this book, and I think the author really writes in a way that don't click with me... </span>
