<span id="freeTextContainer7025454739626642574">I&apos;ve tried twice now to read Ann Rice books, and I just can&apos;t do it. Interview with a Vampire is so incredibly boring. After 100 pages without rousing the slightest interest, I canned it.</span>
  <span id="freeText7025454739626642574" style="display:none">I've tried twice now to read Ann Rice books, and I just can't do it. Interview with a Vampire is so incredibly boring. After 100 pages without rousing the slightest interest, I canned it.</span>
