<span id="freeTextContainer1737133663627643135">I got this book for Christmas and I only recently got into it. I have read <i>Interview with a Vampire</i> and enjoyed it very much. I&apos;m about a 1/4 of the way through <i>The Vampire Lestat</i> and am enjoying that very much. It&apos;s good to get some foundation on Ann Rice&apos;s Vampire Chronicles since I have read several of her other books before these 3. It&apos;s taking me so long to finish it because it is a bulky volume and not easy to lug around when traveling.</span>
  <span id="freeText1737133663627643135" style="display:none">I got this book for Christmas and I only recently got into it. I have read <i>Interview with a Vampire</i> and enjoyed it very much. I'm about a 1/4 of the way through <i>The Vampire Lestat</i> and am enjoying that very much. It's good to get some foundation on Ann Rice's Vampire Chronicles since I have read several of her other books before these 3. It's taking me so long to finish it because it is a bulky volume and not easy to lug around when traveling.</span>
